Parse-BNF version 0.0.1

This uses Parse::Yapp to translate BNF to a nested set of rules and their
embedded alternatives. Naturally it depends upon Parse::Yapp, but it also
uses Regexp::Common to tear apart quoted tokens. This dependency may be removed
later on.


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

Alternatively, to install with Module::Build, you can use the following commands:

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
	./Build test
	./Build install


DEPENDENCIES

None.


